---
title: Feta, Serrano Ham and Butternut Salad With Lentils and Peashoots
description: Tender roasted butternut squash with salty serrano ham and the tart taste of feta is a delicious combination made in foodie heaven. Finish with a drizzle of honey-tahini dressing for a fresh, autumnal-tasting salad.
